cers, LRGs, ELGs, and QSOs. We expect the AbacusHOD framework, in\ncombination with the AbacusSummit simulation suite, to play an important role\nin a simulation-based analysis of the up-coming Dark Energy Spectroscopic\nInstrument (DESI) datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 18:30:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 17:25:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-08"}
